name: David Newbern
bio: Find me on Motortrend’s Faster with Newbern and Cotten and Roadkill every now and then. I love road tripping junky cars and making YouTube videos.

social_posts.post_text:
Two 57 hardtops left for dead. Both  pulled out of junk yards. Both crashed in the front. Both got new chassis’s. Both now daily drivers. @merlinsoldschoolgarage got me hooked the first time we cruised around in his 57. Now we just need to get them together. #1957chevy 
#patina #junkyard #trifivechevy
The new 14k four post @bendpak lift makes the old four post look tiny. The extra height is great. No more ducking to walk around it. #bendpaklift #bendpak #1957 #somuchroomforactivities
Pretty solid lineup. We’re on season 4 of Faster with Finnegan and it’s good. #ricflairmont #1955 #1957 #crusty #dirtyharry #torino
Season 4 of Faster with Finnegan is going to be good! We got some very interesting rides to say the least. #fasterwithfinnegan #honda #1957 #patina #hardtop
#harlemglobetrotters
If you missed this years Holiday Hooptie Challenge it’s coming on at 10 pm eastern standard time tonight on the Motortrend channel. Don’t miss it.
New YouTube video live this morning. We walk around the property and check antifreeze levels in all this junk. I was surprised with the outcome🤦🏻‍♂️🤦🏻‍♂️. Link is in my bio.

My first car was a 1964 Impala at the age of 13. Today I bought that car back. THE car. Not one like it. I’ve owned around 150 cars over the years. We’re back to the one that started it all. Welcome home friend. #blessed #firstcar #impala
Merry Christmas from the NEWBERN’s. I hope everyone has an amazing day.
New YouTube video this morning. I buy back my first car. Check it out. Link is in my bio. Thanks everyone.

This is absolutely incredible. I just got caught up on @merlinsoldschoolgarage and @fabrats jet boat rescue. This boat appeared after the water level went down and had been under water for 30 years. They cleaned it up and got it running again with the engine and pump that was in it. Wow. First few episodes are on @fabrats YouTube and the last few are on @merlinsoldschoolgarage.
2023 is going to be pretty incredible. We got some really cool builds coming soon and I think you guys are gonna dig it. #fasterwithfinnegan #hondaz600coupe #engineswap #sketchy
The finale of the boat rescue is live and it’s good. They track down the original owners and give it back. @merlinsoldschoolgarage and @fabrats killed it. It’s on the fabrats YouTube.

Showed the Impala some love today. Thanks to my buddy @j99fbody we got the dash put back together from where they painted it. Got the seats and the rest of upholstery put back in. Now time to make it run and drive again. #impala #firstcar
My poor Top Kick has been sitting for a few years. As a result the tank is full of rust. It’s okay though, we filtered it and dumped it back in. Runs like new. Kinda.
Off on another adventure. Top Kick is alive after several years. YouTube video to come.
Our ride into town this morning. I need an old school wrecker now. Also, this is the largest Napa I’ve ever been to. #1970 #wrecker #ford #napa

A few photos from the past couple days. Found lots of buried treasures. We drove the Top Kick down to throw a new/used bed on it and ended up leaving it at my buddies shop. We got 7 mpg out of that tall deck 366 and Allison automatic transmission. That junk is coming out and a bigger better combo is going in. All of this is will be on my YouTube.
The 64 is looking goooood. Cotten working his magic.
😳😳 little sneak peek.
Oh my goodness. 🤤🤤🤤
Happy Friday everyone. New YouTube video live this morning. We get the Top Kick running and take a little road trip.
New YouTube video live right now. It’s good and the longest episode to date. I buy my first school bus. Link is in my bio. Thanks everyone.

Just wanted to say thank you to everyone for the support. We hit 27k subscribers today. I’m not gonna lie I was hesitant to start a YouTube channel. @imemilyreeves, @ddspeedshop and the rest of my close friends finally talked me into it. I’m glad I did and we been having fun with it. I’m very appreciative for everyone involved. #blessed #bestfriends
We’re heading to have some fun and destroy some tires. I swapped wheels and tires with the Impala and it’s kinda growing on me.
Fun was had. Tires were shredded. It was a good day.
Where you at @ddspeedshop??
Had fun hanging with @finnegan999 last week. We went up to @paradise_dragstrip and had some fun with the Hot Rods. He just dropped a video on YouTube this morning. Go check it out, it’s good.
Super proud of my boy Lucas and his team. The team was undefeated this season and sealed the deal tonight. #prouddad
New YouTube video live right now. It’s donuts, burnouts for distance and carnage with @finnegan999 and his C-10. Check it out. Link is in my bio.
Happy Friday. Brand new episode live right now on my YouTube channel. We start piecing together a Two Lane Blacktop clone. Link is in my bio. What’s everyone working on this weekend?
We’re two weeks away from season 4 of Faster with Finnegan. I think you guys are gonna enjoy it. We had so much fun. #fasterwithfinnegan #mikecotten #mikefinnegan

Sneak peek of season four of @fasterwithfinnegan coming in two weeks. #ricflairmont Wooooooo makes a comeback. Now time to swap the tires and put him away. #burnoutfordays #chickmagnet #wooo #boost #fasterwithfinnegan

We’re back in Mississippi working on my Top Kick this weekend. @imemilyreeves and @pilotreeves were passing through on their way to #sickweek driving Garfield and hung out with us for a while. #myfriendsareawesome

We just went to the junkyard and bought a school bus that’s been sitting for years. Spent a couple hours and got the 24 valve running. We then road tripped it back to @keyes_kustoms shop and we’re going to rip the engine out and stuff it in the top kick. It will be on my YouTube channel next week. #cummins #schoolbus #engineswap

Wrapping up a fun weekend. Hung out with great friends. We drove a bus from the junkyard to my buddies house. Seen lots of cool stuff and I acquired my first mustang. It was a good weekend. #friends #mustang #draganddrive #cummins

This weekend @midwestimages and myself are hanging out at the Darryl Starbirds national rod and custom car show in Tulsa, Oklahoma. We will be there Friday night and hanging out all day Saturday in the Stu’s fabrication booth. Come by and see us.
I can really appreciate a good tow rig. These folks get it. That cab over🤤. Spotted in Bremen ga. Can we be friends?
Happy Friday. New YouTube video just dropped on my channel. We rescue a bus and have a blast doing it. Link is in my bio or just search David Newbern on YouTube. Hope everyone has an awesome weekend.
Come see us. We’re at the expo center in Tulsa Oklahoma.
We’re at the expo center in Tulsa all day today. Come say hey. This place is incredible.
Damn what an awesome day at the show. Met lots of amazing people and seen lots of beautiful cars and trucks.
My first tri-five purchase of the year. Let’s goooo.
Season four of Faster with Finnegan is live right now. Go check it out. We have an absolute blast. #fasterwithfinnegan #stankdog #yukon
I love junk 😂. That is all.

Brand new episode of Faster with Finnegan is live right now. Go check it out on the Motortrend channel and the Motortrend app. We have some fun with the #rubberduck and make some serious changes to the suspension.
Happy Friday. New YouTube video live right now. We visit a yard with 100 tri-fives in it. Check it out. Link is in my bio.
Todays adventures. YouTube videos to come.

We got the donor 24 valve and Allison transmission from the school bus, two 50 gallon fuel tanks, a crane, t56 transmission, tool boxes, tires, radiator and giant intercooler. Flat bed for the win. Yes we’re going to lower the bed asap. #topkick #cummins #dually #hauler

My buddy @wise5657 is selling his chopper so he can order a blower for his 57. It’s a 81 Kawasaki kz1000 springer rigid, 21” front wheel, 200mm rear tire. Bare bones hot rod bike. Asking $5500 bucks. Located in west Georgia. Check out #blasphemi in the early stages and #gameover before it was finished.
Brand new episode of @fasterwithfinnegan right now on the Motortrend app and channel. This one is kind of special. Big changes take place and we have a very special guest. Check it out.
Just one more reason I need a wrecker in my life. YouTube video coming this weekend.
I promise we have more fun than the others. #tri-five #1957chevy #dadbod thanks to @ddspeedshop for the art work lol.
Brand new YouTube episode live on my channel right now. We rip the engine out of the school bus with the wrecker. Check it out. Link is in my bio
We went junkin this weekend and seen all kinds of great stuff. YouTube videos to come. #damnitdan #junkinwithdan #junkyard #rust @ddspeedshop @wise5657 @topkick366

Had a great weekend in North Carolina with @ddspeedshop @wise5657 @topkick366 checking out a yard with over 1000 classics in it. I didn’t have any luck finding a car to drag home but I did find some cool stuff to put in front of the shop! #realmower #cocacola #pepsi #theycallmefrank I just need an old gas pump now.

Happy Tuesday. I’m super pumped about todays episode. This was @midwestimages and I first episode with the new changes. This was a ton of work and lots of “ I have no idea if this will work” moments. We just dove in and gave it our best. Cotten was an animal driving this thing around the track. I’m extremely grateful for our team and the hard work they put in. It’s live on the Motortrend app right now and will be on cable later today. I hope you guys like it.  #Honda #fasterwithfinnegan #rearengine

If you don’t have the Motortrend app that’s okay. Tonight at 9/8c it will be on Motortrendtv. It’s the Bozo episode and no, I’m not talking about Cotten. We build a 72 Honda 600 coupe and it turned out pretty wild. We call it Bozo the clown car. Thanks to so many for all the support. You guys rock.
Put some fresh 275s on the Impala. Can’t wait to drive this thing. #firstcar #impala #tri-five #1957 #cragars

Well, it’s Monday and it’s kind of late in the day. I started this upload on Friday in hopes I could go live with it Sunday morning. My internet really sucks to say the least. Anyway, brand new YouTube episode live right now. If you’re looking for an old cab over you need to watch this video. We get to see lots of neat stuff. Link is in my bio. Thanks everyone

It’s timeeee. Cotten and myself score a sweet 68 Torino and try our hand at this Pro Touring stuff. With a small budget and just two days we were able to make enough changes and bring some life into this hot rod. What a blast. Watch it on the Motortrend app right now or tonight on the Motortrend channel at 9/8c. Also, if you ever get the chance to rip your car around an auto cross, do it.

Next Tuesday is going to be insane.  Lots of crazy stuff happens but the biggest thing for me is hanging out with @goldbergsgarage. We bring #ricflairmont back and he puts on a hell of a show. You guys are going to love it.
#gatlinburg
Nice day to clean up some engines.
It’s time to start our guys weekend. We gotta drop the mustang off @larabellracecars to get the 8.50 cage installed and then we’re off to the beach for a few days to fish and relax.

Brand new YouTube video live this morning. @ddspeedshop comes down to hang out and we travel to North Carolina to check out a yard with over 1000 cars and trucks buried in the woods. Link is in my bio.
It’s been a great and relaxing few days. Now time to get back to the shop and finish up some projects. #biloxi #gators #fishing #beach
The 64 runs. One step closer to power tour.
It’s late but that’s okay. We just went to town and back and man this car rides so good. Can’t wait for power tour!
The children out here getting some Sun. #impala #firstcar #1957 #patina

@larabellracecars just finished this badass 8:50 cage in the new car. The quality of work is absolutely incredible. Now its time to throw it together and meet up with @lylebarnett to have some fun. #foxbody #coupe #boost
The variety of automobiles here is pretty good. #impala #mustang #lambo #topkick #dragkota
Did some car shuffling today. Finished up some much needed maintenance. #lambo #scamborghini #opel #funnycar #1964impala #myfirstcar
It’s gonna be a long night.

Today was officially day one of filming Faster with Newbern and Cotten. @taylorreimerr was nice enough to give @midwestimages some driving tips and the little Honda we call Bozo surprised all of us. What a day!

In just 3 days we took this shell of a body and built us a race car. It’s got an all aluminum LS engine backed by a powerglide built to handle whatever we throw at it from the guys @gearstarpro. The cage was custom built by @larabellracecars. Jeff over @mosspeedshop saved the day with some parts we were missing and @midwestimages, @dasbig and myself got it all together and now the fun begins! Huge thanks to all my friends that pitched in to help.
@harrellengineanddyno is pushing the up arrow this morning
Not a bad day at work! #newcar #beermoney
Let’s try this again. @harrellengineanddyno hit the up arrow and let’s make some power.
Scamborghini.
Went out for a little birthday cruise. Pops said I was number 1. Hope everyone enjoys the weekend!

Hands down best purchase I’ve ever made was my tractor. It never failed me and it’s been a huge help over the last several years. Today we upgraded to a larger one and I hope it’s as good as the first. #kubota #tractor #mykindoftoy
Nice little gathering near the house this morning.

New YouTube video live this morning. My first car is alive! We install the new interior and get my 1964 Impala running after sitting for years. We finally get to drive it. Link is in my bio. Happy Sunday! #impala #firstcar
Guess what Roadkill vehicle is coming back…

My dad turned 80 years old over the weekend. He’s 100% the reason I’m into cars and have made it where I am today. I grew up traveling to different car shows every weekend. I was definitely blessed with good parents. My childhood was pretty amazing. Happy Birthday Dad.
Happy Tuesday! New YouTube video live this morning. We tend to break stuff, or catch it on fire. Check out some behind the scenes repairs! Link is in my bio.
It’s been a crazy two weeks and we’re not done yet. Faster with Newbern and Cotten is in full swing. We’re attempting some pretty ridiculous stuff.
Pigpen is gonna be rowdy. Upgraded chassis and an LS7!

So many people were curious where Pigpen went. Our show runner Dustin got his hands on it after @davidfreiburger and @finnegan999 got done filming with it. We had it shipped here and we cut up the s15 chassis and put it under pigpens body and installed the ls7 from the Dirt Every Day motorhome. This thing is gonna be nasty with 630 hp.
I’m officially in love with pigpen. It’s low, fast and has just the right amount of patina

I been keeping this secret for a while. @ddspeedshop and myself came up with a plan to surprise our buddy Brandon by completely upgrading everything on his car. @speedwaymotorsinc got on board and away we went. I finally let him in on it because we have 3 days till power tour and we got a lot of work to do. #builtwithspeedwaymotors
Power tour prep in full force. We got all the help. @ddspeedshop @simons_powerhouse @howes_it_doin_garage @keyes_kustoms @wise5657 @speedwaymotorsinc #builtwithspeedwaymotors

The @roadkillshow 57 we rescued last year in Texas is almost ready for Hot Rod Power Tour. @speedwaymotorsinc wanted in on the project so we all teamed up and surprised my buddy @wise5657 by installing an LS, T56 magnum, ford 9” rear, new floors, wiring, gauges, radiator, brakes etc. The best part of this build is all my friends coming to hang out and wrench. I love building hot rods, especially really crappy ones. #builtwithspeedwaymotors #1957 #patina
Good turnout today. We’re ready! Hot Rod Power Tour starts tomorrow! See y’all there.

We’re officially ready for Hot Rod Power Tour. We leave in the morning for Atlanta Motor Speedway. Huge thanks to all our friends for helping out with this one. @ddspeedshop @simons_powerhouse @howes_it_doin_garage @nickfarris53 @topkick366 @wise5657 @rips_rides @heavy427sideoiler
See y’all in Atlanta.
Great first day of Hot Rod Power Tour. The 57 is doing great. Heading to Columbia SC tomorrow for day two.

We’re on the road for day 2 of Hod Rod Power Tour 2023. We will be parked in the @speedwaymotorsinc booth with @ddspeedshop and @simons_powerhouse. Come see us. @midwestimages @ddspeedshop and myself will be doing a meet and greet this evening. Meanwhile, this tri-five is doing great. We just filled up for the first time since leaving the house and we’re getting 14.5 mpg. Engine combo is 2002 all aluminum 5.3 liter, @holleyperformance sniper tunnel ram with two 450 cfm carburetors on top, Tremec Magnum 6 speed and a @speedwaymotorsinc ford 9” out back with 410 gears. She’s a cruiser. See y’all at the venue!
Cruising through small towns is one of the best things about Hot Rod Power Tour. #hrpt2023 #somadd #1955 #1957 #tri-five
We’re hiding @Wirecare road rations this week. Go give them a follow and take a pic with the 57 and tag us when you find it. We’re in Columbia SC right now. Let’s go…
Give @wirecare_inc a follow and look out for some goodies stashed along the way.
The best part of Hot Rod Power Tour is hanging out with my friends, even if it means working on junk on the side of the road. We’re about to be at Rockingham Speedway in a few. Come see us.
We have stashed two @wirecare_inc road rations at the venue here at Rockingham Speedway. Give @wirecare_inc a follow and be sure and tag us if you find them.
We took #Badmaro for a rip around Rockingham Speedway with @alextaylorracing in pursuit 😂

We did it! My buddies and I built a junky 57 Chevy in 3 days and drove it through 4 different states with zero issues. We got 16-18 mpg depending on who was driving😂. Huge thanks to @speedwaymotorsinc for throwing all the parts at it. @holleyperformance for the badass intake and carb setup and @wirecare_inc for allowing us to have a little fun hiding road rations. Can’t wait for next year.

I love junky cars. Especially 
Tri-fives.
Just gonna leave this right here 😂 @gearstarpro @midwestimages
Big things are happening in the shop. #fasterwithnewbernandcotten
All the action from Hot Rod Power Tour is live right now. New YouTube episode featuring lots of familiar faces and badass cars. Link is in my bio.
The famous Pigpen from Roadkill is back and it’s bad. We stuffed the 630 hp LS7 from the Dirt Every Day motorhome in it. You will see it on an upcoming episode of Faster with Newbern and Cotten.

@midwestimages and myself built the worlds first mega lamborghini countach. There is a couple of monster truck/Lambo’s out there but not any actual cars that’s I’ve found.  It’s on 2.5 ton Rockwell axles with 4 wheel steer, @scs.probell.performanceracing reverse rotation case, @gearstarpro level 4 th400 transmission, GM crate small block Chevy, 58” @mickeythompsontires. My buddy Richard and son Rich helped out with the chassis and @dirthead_dave hooked us up with some parts from the #ranchota from DED. It will be on Motortrend starting in September and will be in the background of my YouTube videos going forward 😂.
Problem solved!
#Pigpen is looking good.

I haven’t been to a local cruise in in probably 15 years. I’m always working or at events. We made it happen this weekend. We brought the whole fleet out. The Impala has never been to a show. We couldn’t leave it out.
Productive day! Got a couple of sweet projects coming back.
It felt good to get all the hot rods out of the shop and go cruise. Definitely need to make this a regular thing! #1957chevy #1957 #1964impala #impala #tunnelram #patina
Happy Sunday.  New YouTube video live this morning. We bring another tri-five home and hit up a local cruise in. Link is in my bio. #1955 #tri-five #survivor

I’ve always wanted to build a Baja bug. @midwestimages made it happen for us. @cameron_steele16 was nice enough to let us use his shop for 3 days so we could build it. #fasterwithnewbernandcotten #baja #volkswagen
Fun was had. I wanna build a v8 powered rail buggy now! @midwestimages @cameron_steele16 #fasterwithnewbernandcotten #baja

My job definitely doesn’t suck. Mega lambo is ready to rock. Built in four days on a custom chassis. 2.5 ton Rockwell axles, scs reverse case, 58” Mickey Thompson tires, Gearstar th400 transmission, four wheel steer.

Thats a wrap for this season of Faster with Newbern and Cotten. Coming to Motortrend this September. Huge thanks to everyone for all the support and to our awesome crew for going along with all of our crazy ideas. #fasterwithnewbernandcotten #scamborghini #megatruck #livakilla #twittysmudbog

Project ramp truck is on the way home with us. 1968 c50. 

If anyone has a ramp bed for sale let me know. Otherwise we’re gonna build one from scratch.
Quick little getaway before school starts back.

Who’s going to Roadkill Nights?? @midwestimages and myself will be road tripping #ricflairmont along side our buddies @finnegan999 @davidfreiburger and @stevedulcich from Georgia to Michigan! The drive should be good with a powerglide and 373 gears with a short tire. I might do a gear change before hand. See y’all there.

#ricflairmont #dumpsterfire #bangshiftcougar 

We’re on our way to Roadkill Nights. See y’all there.
Been a hell of a trip so far. Cars are doing great. Burn outs every time we stop. #becauseroadkill
Cars are running great but for some reason all three are gonna need tires before we actually make it to Roadkill Nights!
The word is out. It’s official. We’re coming back for more. Huge thanks to everyone for all the support. We got some wild episodes coming soon. See y’all at Roadkill Nights!
And that’s a wrap for Roadkill Nights 2023!

This week was freaking epic. Three roadkill cars made it from Atlanta to Pontiac Michigan with no road side repairs needed all while beating the absolute crap out of them every chance we got. Damn, what a week. #becauseroadkill #ricflairmont #bangshiftcougar #daytona #roadkillnights2023 #roadkillnights #burnouts
We’re Texas bound for another project car. We’re also delivering @mobiletechlucky new to him trailer. Fingers crossed this deal lives for the next 16 hours.
One last trip to Big Spring before the property gets sold. It’s bitter sweet. Got another project and loaded the car and truck down with parts. #ripdickie
My sons new ride. #1957 #tri-five #crewcab #firstcar
Got to hang out with my buddy @keithturk200 yesterday and see the famous land speed Camaro in person. Also, got to see his other toys. The man is a freaking genius.
Man, I love this car. My son and I went cruising for several hours yesterday. On the way home he says “can we make a few laps around town before we go home?” Hell yes we can!
New YouTube video live this fine Sunday morning. The K5 blazer project is almost ready for the streets. Check it out. Link is in my bio. #k5blazer #lifted #squarebody
I just picked up one of the nicest rust free 1929 model a’s I’ve ever seen. Not a single pinhole of rust. Now let’s get it back to Georgia.
Huge savings. Go buy stuff.
🤷🏻‍♂️🤷🏻‍♂️🤷🏻‍♂️ upgrades are underway!

A lot happened today. The 57 got a little upgrade. I need to round up some hardware tomorrow and connect the fuel lines and we’re ready to rip @finnegan999 got me hooked on ramp trucks and roots blowers. #1957 #tri-five #supercharger #crusty
Bought this 671 blower straight off the display shelf @summitracing and dropped it straight on my 454. It’s time to party.
I need some mountain trails and a little mud in my near future. #hondatalon #mud #memories
Best thing in life is being a Dad. I’m blessed with some good kids. My daughter starts driving soon and my 8 year old son is all about Hot Rods. Also, the 57 is just about ready to smoke some tires!
My happy place! #1957 #tri-five #blown #boost #stickshift
Happy Sunday. New YouTube video live this morning. Click the link in my bio and check it out 👍
Throwing another 57 Chevy together from the Texas trip. This is the last one. Time to undercoat it. The gantry crane from @harborfreight is a tool I didn’t realize I needed as bad as I did.
Tomorrow is the big day! Faster with Newbern and Cotten is coming to the Motortrend channel so be sure an check it out. We had an absolute blast and built some really fun projects. @midwestimages

Don’t forget, tonight on the Motortrend channel at 10/9 c you can see @lylebarnett go up against his toughest competitor yet, Cotten. They have a trash talking contest and then afterwards, beer money does what beer money does best, gap fools. On this episode I was the fool and it was badass! #fasterwithnewbernandcotten #foxbody #gapped #boost #turbo #procharger #beermoney

It’s the return of Pigpen! Remember this truck from the early seasons of @roadkillshow? After the Roadkill episode the truck got sold to a staff member.  @midwestimages and myself got our hands on it and stuffed a 630 hp ls7 in it backed by a @gearstarpro 4l80. We took our s15 from the very first episode and used the chassis under Pigpen. Check it out on the Motortrend app or watch tonight on the Motortrend channel at 10/9 c.

It’s getting down to the wire. We’re leaving tomorrow for Cruisin’ the Coast. The whole crew will be there all week and Dan is bringing shirts. Find us and let’s hang out!  @ddspeedshop @midwestimages @larabellracecars @keyes_kustoms @wise5657 @simons_powerhouse
We’re Biloxi bound! Cruisin the Coast is our favorite car show. Lucas has been counting down the days for months now. Let’s goooo.
Cruisin the coast has officially started!
Cruisin’ the Coast 2023. #tri-five #nova #gasser #blower #boost #1957

Bringing back some memories this year in Biloxi. My friend Mike owned this 39 Chevy back when I was just a kid. He recently bought it back after 20 years. Cruisin the Coast was everyone’s favorite show so it’s good to have it back around.

Brand new episode of Faster with Newbern and Cotten on the Motortrend channel right now. We find an old cop car and road race it @willow_springs_raceway. We finish by blowing the intake off with a nitrous backfire. #fasterwithnewbernandcotten #p71
Crusty out in the parking lot showing off the new jewelry. #1957 #supercharged #boost #tri-five #crusty #cruisinthecoast

It’s also live right now on the Motortrend app! 

Huge thanks to everyone for all the support. This build was really fun and I can’t wait to do it again.
I surprised Lucas with a Jr Dragster last week. His birthday isn’t for another month but this was a little difficult to hide.
Today was fun! #fasterwithnewbernandcotten @claymillican @midwestimages

Just got one of the biggest surprises ever! Was supposedly on the way to a race track and we turned back because the camera crew forgot something. Pull up and the Anderson boys are at my house. I was completely speechless. @midwestimages surprised me and we’re now building something to compete with these boys! It will be epic.

It’s the season finale of Faster with Newbern and Cotten. The mega Lambo is live on the Motortrend app right now and hits the Motortrend channel tonight at 10/9c. We had an absolute blast building this rig and hanging out with @liva_killa. Russell is a legend and a mad man behind the wheel of that K-5 blazer.
Roll call- who’s going to Sema? Cotten and myself will be in the techflex booth Wednesday and Thursday. Come by and say hello. We will also be roaming the streets of Vegas pretty much every night.

First fuel stop in the Hot Rod Garage vette. @luckys_garage and @tangelo96 had some fun with this thing about 3 years ago and it’s been in storage ever since. I also snagged a new to me Drag Week trailer. #c5 #corvette #roadtrip #eastboundanddown

Been a pretty good trip so far. I noticed the car had excessive valve train noise when I got it. Made it all the way to El Paso and decided to pull the valve covers and check lash. Installed longer push rods and it runs really smooth now an zero valve train noise. While I was changing the oil I noticed a leak from the rear. One of the brake lines got into the half shaft and busted. Got it all fixed and it’s like a new car. Kinda. East bound and down. Huge thanks to my buddy @55chevygas for introducing me to this badass speed shop. They saved my trip.
